organisation_title: Lycée Félix Esclangon. Comité du Patrimoine Manosquin. Herbier G. Fenoul
organisation_description: Herbarium of the late nineteenth and early twentieth more than 6,000 specimens. All sheets were photographed and the databasing in Sonnerat system is in progress. Gustave Fenoul own collections and many exchanges: flora exciccata par Ch.Magnier, Sté helvétique... Gift of Gustave Fenoul family to Lycée de Manosque. Administrated by Comité Manosquin.
